Chelyabinsk Zinc Advances Most in Week After Income Doubles

-- B y   J a s o n   C o r c o r a n
-- 
2011-04-28T07:03:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-28/chelyabinsk-zinc-advances-most-in-week-after-income-doubles.html
Chelyabinsk Zinc Plant (CHZN)  jumped the
most in almost a week after the company said 2010 net income
more than doubled from the year before to 1.41 billion rubles
($51.2 million).  The stock climbed 1.5 percent to 138.4 rubles by 10:47 a.m.
in Moscow, its biggest intraday advance since April 22.  Sales rose 16 percent in the period to 11.8 billion rubles,
the company said in a statement. 